div.summary:
Reports the election of officers on December 14 for the Friendship Fire
                    Co.: President--Maurer; Vice Pres.--Seiders; Treasurer--Huber;
                    Secretary--Jarrett; Directors--Garwick, Henneberger and Zarman; Chief
                    Pipeman--Ludwig; Assistant Pipemen--Earley and Bence; Standing Committee--Remp,
                    Smith, Perry, Seiders, and Gordon; Hose Attachees--Remp, Perry, Stumbaugh,
                    Lightcap and Bert; Hose Guards--Seiders, Remp, Zarman, Myers and Frederick;
                    Auditors--Wright, King and Etter; Axemen--Kunce, Duke and Henneberger;
                    Collector--Jarrett; Superintendent--Henneberger.
